Package: scoredevr
Type: Package
Title: to build a score card
Version: 0.1.0
Date:03-03-2019 
Author: Demyd Dzyuban
Maintainer: Demyd Dzyuban <demydd@gmail.com>
Description: The package is developed to automate all key aspects of score card development.
             Procedures are built to save all key data of all score card development steps.
             The data are saved to .csv files and quite easy to read by other useres of score cards.
             The package contains the graphical option to present some key indicators.
